# 9.46: Disability in Narrative 

Listen [here](http://www.writingexcuses.com/2014/11/09/writing-excuses-9-46-disability-in-narrative/). 

**Prompt:** Go to tvtropes.org and look up “Blind People.” Read some of the many tropes (Disability Superpower, Blind Black Guy, and Blind Mistake, just to name three)  then write a blind character without using those tropes.
